title: Super Eagles have no business losing to DR Congo -Pinnick
text:
15:55 CET Super Eagles have no business losing to DR Congo -Pinnick - www.ghanasoccernet.com 
NFF President Amaju Pinnick has called on the Super Eagles to finish licking their wounds after they were beaten by the Leopards in an exhibition match on Thursday night. 
The build- up to the game against the Central Africans was overshadowed by a well- publicized dispute between coach Sunday Oliseh and Nigeria 's most capped player Vincent Enyeama, and the goalkeeper had to call time on his international career.
